</p><p class="para">Of course, No. 2 knew what happened. No. 16 had detonated her fusion reactor in hopes of exterminating the enemies, along with Lily, Dahlia, and Margaret. Infected No. 21, who was still hacking, and Anemone, who had stayed behind to kill her. If they pulled back now, all those deeds would be meaningless.
</p><p class="para">"But I'm... sad. This is..."
