</p><p class="para">It wasn't only No. 4 that wanted to change the subject. Everybody was trying to find a lighter subject to talk about, especially because they were trapped in such a small space.
</p><p class="para">"Simulated memories, huh?"
</p><p class="para">Rose's eyes lightened up a little. From that, No. 2 could tell that her simulated memories were filled with happiness.
