<br>"<i>We were watching you, this whole time.</i>"
</p><p class="para">The two girls tilted their heads to the side in a mirrored fashion. The girl on the right tilted her head toward the right, and the girl on the left toward the left. The way they acted made No. 2 very uncomfortable.
