<br>"<i>Why do you want to die so much?</i>"
</p><p class="para">"Don't be stupid!" screamed Rose. "It's because of you fools, isn't it?! You're the ones that stole Earth away from humanity!"
</p><p class="para">The girls ignored the accusations, and instead started giggling.
</p><p class="para">"<i>You were only created to die.</i>"
<br>"<i>You were only sent to Earth to die.</i>"
</p><p class="para">Wanting to drown out the girls, No. 2 raised her voice in a frenzy. "That's wrong! We came to fight! We weren't created to die!"
</p><p class="para">The girls scoffed at her reply.
</p><p class="para">"<i>Even though humans abandoned you?</i>"
<br>"<i>Even though you're being used?</i>"
