</p><p class="para">It was an uncharacteristically intense shriek from No. 4. She was swinging her sword as hard as she could. Perhaps that's why the girls dodged her attacks so easily.
</p>

<p class="para">"<i>We hacked into your servers and found some interesting information.</i>"<br>
"<i>It's very important, so listen carefully.</i>"<br>
